      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Stopped at a scenic viewpoint, \nasked someone nearby to take a photo
        the picture turned out blurry tho."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[1]'
      value: "Hiked 2 km to see a waterfall \u2014 \nit was completely dry."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Scenic viewpoint is under renovation, \nbut still stopped just to see
        the fence anyway."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[3]'
      value: "Visited a temple because the sign said,\n\u201CMonk gives accurate
        lottery numbers.\u201D"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Stopped at a souvenir market, \nbought some durians \u2014\nand now
        the whole car smells."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[5]'
      value: "Visited a sheep farm \u2014 \nall the sheep were hiding from the sun,
        \nso we only get to see the birds..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[6]'
      value: "Found a cute roadside caf\xE9,\nwent in alone, \ncame out with a car-full
        of souvenirs."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[7]'
      value: "Entered a national park, \ndrove really far in \u2014 \nended up with
        no signal \ntook us a while to get out."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[8]'
      value: "Checked in at a famous social media spot \u2014 \nturned out it was
        the size of a milk carton."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2098135986438730418, guid: 15f09d4736e07b0438b0c18c0f3aeddf, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'descriptionVariants.Array.data[9]'
      value: "Went to see the sea of mist, \narrived at noon \u2014 \nthere was only
        the sun..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
